Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:14.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:21.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Yano-san, Yoshida-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:27.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm experiencing the very thing I've always longed for!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.11,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:35.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start crying if I stop contracting my eyebrow muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, if you're happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, you don't have to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:51.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely look gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well take advantage of that appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.58,0:01:58.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take advantage of my appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:07.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:10.90,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:25.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:26.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who were you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on Ryu, she's a classmate, you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really leave much of an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:36.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do, in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:39.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma Sawako. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:43.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad with names.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:44.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:51.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So much has changed since Kazehaya-kun chose to sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:56.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't decide on a name for the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you pick one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:10.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro Martinez. Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:15.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our sub teacher; why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's  Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:18.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(507,695)}He's supposed to be our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(527,695)}He's got problems at home, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:24.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filling in indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand slam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Problems at home? Is this because of Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he made her do stuff over the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:37.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Zen mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:42.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:05.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being tough again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:09.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it would be a good rumor if Pin survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:33.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standup comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.95,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:44.72,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is my pulse different from when Sensei was staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:50.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known Ryu forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:53.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in middle school together along with Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Chizu in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sat close to each other, so we became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:04.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Kazehaya, has he always been so cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:11.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been nice to people who don't fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's always the leader amongst the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And popular with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:18.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good person in middle school too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was this huge fight over him amongst the girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:29.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those who realized he probably doesn't like that sort of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:32.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,established the “Kazehaya Belongs to Everyone Accord.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“The People's Kazehaya.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious? That's so retarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:46.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He moves people, captures their hearts and brings them to action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.71,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:53.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that there's a lot of girls from our middle school here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:01.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They came to see him from another class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone stay behind after school and write up the attendance form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push it on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zen always does his.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:18.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then, I'll choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No one wants to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well that's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't take long with two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:34.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind helping if Kazehaya is doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone wants to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:42.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I–If everyone else wants to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd do it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:55.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say that out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:07:00.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? What's with this mushy stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the office!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One sec, I have to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:58.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I slipped out while Pin went to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've given me all sorts of opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:16.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:21.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe everyone's waiting for a chance to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend me your pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha–
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya Shouta of 1-D, come to the office immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get here within one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone's going to know everything about your embarrassing past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:05.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I–
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun was here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirano-san and Endou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:29.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe everyone's waiting for a chance to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:30.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:35.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would it be okay if we talked for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not angry, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:05.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always look so angry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:08.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you liked being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:14.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you were happy being able to talk to Yoshida-san or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always said hello to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we got sort of curious and came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kazehaya said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come inside? Don't just stand out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always doing our chores anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:37.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the sensitive type?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did people call you before “Sadako”?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:47.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I liked it when people called me “Zashiki Warashi.”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:50.20,KimiTodo-Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Zashiki Warashi is a mythical creature that brings good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liked that? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so freaked out when you were that ghost in the test of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly thought you were a real ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun gave me opportunities,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:07.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,and things are slowly changing around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirano-san and Endou-san helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:28.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Kazehaya-kun, I'm changing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's you giving me the strength to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:43.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, Yoshida, Hirano, Endou–they're all being moved by your diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:51.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one moving me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:55.46,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving someone like Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have thought it possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:07.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd be so happy if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:21.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Hirano-chan and Endou-chan helped you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:29.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you both talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they talked to me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:43.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's trying to say that it's because you worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true, though, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad things are working out for you{you're getting what you deserve}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:56.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky to have such nice people to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This? Horror stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horror stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:08.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that, maybe, I could live up to your expectations with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako? Horror stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I kind of want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pragmatist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pragmatic or weird? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:23.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything up until now will be on the midterm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bug—there's a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:59.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've gotten a note. I didn't know it was for Yano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.75,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:53.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand was shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.78,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm done taking this to the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:02.05,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home, get changed…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.26,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:10.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:20.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a French doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:34.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the high point of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Maru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My baiting plan is a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you usually be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, not before exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:32.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually have fun fantasizing—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:34.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, fantasizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:40.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, say the person next to me is having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:45.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think, “maybe she's having trouble with this,”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or “how can I explain it so that she would understand?”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:54.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually I would get a lot of studying done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:01.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, have you told anyone about Maru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:11.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, we're the only ones who know about how we found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling anyone then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:24.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be the only one who's seen him smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,or has been smiled at by him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:30.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, I get it all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:36.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope tomorrow will be a good day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can you help me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the person next to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:51.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't this “なに”, even though it's “what”?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This “what” is called a relative pronoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:59.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you, are you actually studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:02.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these two phrases are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one and this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:07.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's helping them study.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:10.28,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you translate these two together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:14.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually got Yoshida to answer a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help us too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this works the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:40.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.88,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,She should just use the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:46.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you help us again sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made myself useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:58.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She—She's smi—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:21.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:38.59,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,About yesterday, that was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All those people who helped. You got your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:50.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came true when you asked me to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have gotten sick of hearing it by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, he's talking to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:13.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was the only one that knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit bummed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let me have this one....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:26.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was the first time I've ever seen her smile like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:35.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks pretty normal when she's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.30,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:38.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida's that thin-eyed girl right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:42.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the ex-delinquent who used to be in a detention center.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:46.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that other Yano girl's a real slut, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:49.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did a hundred guys in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, that's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:53.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:57.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:57.94,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, who told you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who started that rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:11.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:28.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Words misplaced;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:30.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,feelings miscommunicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:33.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Rumors
